occupancy on <A HREF="HELP_DC065.asp">Address Details (DC065)</A>.</P>
<P><H3>Landlord Type: </H3>select from the drop-down list 
whether this is Housing Authority, Local Authority or Private Landlord
<P></P>
<P><H3>Name: </H3>this must be completed to proceed, as it may 
be necessary to check the information provided and obtain a landlord’s 
reference.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Rent: </H3>enter the amount of rent paid in the field – 
this may be used to assess affordability and may also be confirmed by a 
reference Address and
<P></P>
